{"tid":635201,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分完手一定放底？","createTime":"2018-04-20T02:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T15:08:40.000Z","uid":109224,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"42d335e99f6de79c45c5616b09b9a6270b85ad77","tid":635201,"uid":109224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T02:48:40.000Z","msg":"剛分手，三年四個月，仍然相愛，但因我不夠上進，想像不到將來而和平分開。眼見各位都話分手後，傷夠喊夠，就好放手，不要糾纏不清。<br />\n我卻覺得，為自為她，改變自己，再一次追求她，又何嘗不可以。<br />\n即使她已忘記我，也只是重頭開始，當初也是這樣，憑咩變得更好後追唔到。<br />\n即使於事無補，已經太遲，我也盡力了，沒有遺憾。<br />\n即使她已得到她的幸福，我也令自己變得更好了，我會感激她,祝福她。"},{"pid":"5345f9a0e0e28665dae5dadb29b5585cc9244996","tid":635201,"uid":109224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"宜家問題在如何調整心情，不是為她，而係為自己奮鬥。"},{"pid":"2415eade71e96972a8b679a4c46c01a9e9db7c63","tid":635201,"uid":182362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔上進呀"},{"pid":"9b5c6dd7700e4da0abc0eb97dec3b21993e8cfdd","tid":635201,"uid":46128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9385ee3d73a98ae2780c8bad28c7e42699e653a","tid":635201,"uid":109224,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2415eade71e96972a8b679a4c46c01a9e9db7c63","tid":635201,"uid":182362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:01:08.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔上進呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:13:04.000Z","msg":"對現在太滿意，不思進取，錯在我"},{"pid":"fa02c12786553e7c1e9b622cb4f03935dac466a3","tid":635201,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"共鳴"},{"pid":"3f9ca02ef10a45ba17ecbd7030ef13167419c82d","tid":635201,"uid":77769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a472ce4b3a3640400c54b811bfa300cc06597d","tid":